kalische Anwendungen lassen sich damit widerspruchsfrei verstehen. Die Grundeigenschaften der Atomkerne werden in verständlichen Modellen entwickelt. Ein abschließender Überblick über den Kosmos der elementaren Teilchen und der Grundkräfte macht deutlich, dass es auf diesem Feld noch vieles zu entdecken gibt.  aThis four-part series for physics teachers in training addresses the principles of physics in a clear and compact way. The experienced lecturer confronts familiar falsehoods held by students with explanatory side notes, conveying examples from everyday life, technological applications, and the historical development of science in consolidation topics. Volume 3 comprises atomic, nuclear, and quantum physics.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAtomphysik. 4aKernphysik. 4aMehrelektronensysteme. 4aRadioaktivität. 7aSCIENCE / Physics / Atomic & Molecular.2bisacsh  aAtomic physics.  amulti-electron systems.  anuclear physics.  aradioactivity.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry, Mat.Sc, Geosc 2022z9783110993219oZDB-23-DPC0 cEPUBz97831104691890 cprintz978311046890840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311046897740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110468977423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110468977/original  a978-3-11-076682-0  DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DPCb2022